      params.totalStableDebt,
      params.totalVariableDebt,
      vars.currentVariableBorrowRate,
      params.averageStableBorrowRate
    ).rayMul(vars.supplyUsageRatio).percentMul(
        PercentageMath.PERCENTAGE_FACTOR - params.reserveFactor
